  "stem": "<p class=\"stem_paragraph \">In the&nbsp;<span class=\"italic\"><span class=\"italic \">xy</span></span>-plane, the graph of <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"2 x squared, minus 6 x, plus 2 y squared, plus 2 y, equals 45\"></span> is a circle. What is the radius of the circle?</p>\n",
